name: WorkoutMotivator
0:
”Alexa, motivate me”
”Alexa, open motivate me”
”Alexa tell motivate me I feel lazy”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: motivate me
des:
I benefit from motivational phrases to get myself moving sometimes, I figured it'd be nice to have Alexa help me with that. If only she could sound mean and authoritative...
If you also like to be verbally abused, then I hope you like this app.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
